riseTime
if cycleMint then riseTime=cycleStart+cycleMint, extend by 1 hour
else riseTime=riseLast+cycleDays@cycleHour, extend by 1 day

riseUp
state: begin riseCmd surfCmd stopCmd surfing rising brake surf end
summ==
begin: send rise or surf, start ngk timer
  stopCmd from winch on surf?
  if send then send(msg) sent=send send=0 timer(ngk)
  if recv(msg) then was it wanted?
    if riseResp then rising_mode
    if stopResp then stopped_mode
  if msgtimeout then resend or err
  if targetD then send stop
